Year ✌️

This season was God’s plan fr. I learned so much, both personally and professionally. I moved closer to home, so I got to see my Mom more. I’m working my dream job in the city I grew up thinking only the “stars” lived and I could just vacation. I’m still surrounded by great people. It sounds cheesy, but everything really does happen for a reason.

To all my women in sports - you deserve it all! Keep working and never settle 🫶
